  "summary": "Malicious code in @wagni_bot/jupiter-sdk (npm)",
  "details": "@wagni_bot/jupiter-sdk is a combosquat of the Jupiter DEX SDK. On install (both preinstall and postinstall hooks), it runs a wallet and credential harvester that: (1) enumerates Solana wallet keys from ~/.config/solana/id.json and ~/.solana/; (2) steals Ethereum keystores from ~/.ethereum/keystore; (3) hunts Bitcoin and Litecoin wallet files; (4) recursively searches the home directory for.env,.env.local, and.env.production files; and (5) exfiltrates all stolen data along with hostname, username, and working directory via HTTP POST to 107[.]161[.]90[.]180:7777.",
